<div class="column1"><span class="cushycms">The Head, Clara &amp; Maria Public Library is located in the municipal building at:
<p><strong>15 Township Hall Road<br />
Stonecliffe, Ontario, Canada<br />
K0J 2K0</strong></p>

<p><strong><span class="leadtext">Phone:</span> (613) 586-1950</strong> - if there is no answer, please leave a message, messages will be returned within 24 hrs; &nbsp;&nbsp;(for&nbsp;immediate assistance, phone&nbsp;613-586-2526)</p>

<p><strong><span class="leadtext">Fax:</span> (613) 586-2596</strong></p>

<p><strong><span class="leadtext">Email:</span></strong> <a href="mailto:hcmlibra13@gmail.com">hcmlibra13@gmail.com</a></p>

<p><strong><span class="leadtext">Website:</span></strong> <a href="http://www.hcmpubliclibrary.ca">www.hcmpubliclibrary.ca</a></p>

<p><strong><span class="leadtext">Hours:</span></strong></p>

<p><strong>&nbsp;&nbsp;Monday: 8:30 - 4:00<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;Tuesday: 8:30 - 4:00, 6:00 - 8:30<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;Wednesday: 8:30 - 4:00<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;Thursday: CLOSED<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;Friday: 8:30 - 4:00<br />
&nbsp;&nbsp;Saturday: 12:30 - 3:00</strong></p>

<p>The library may be accessed through the municipal office side entrance.</p>
</span>
