<div class="column1"><span class="cushycms"><ul class="newslist">
	<li><strong><a href="library_services.asp#museumpasses">The library has added to its museum passes</a>.</strong> They now have a <a href="http://nature.ca/en/home" target="_blank">Nature Card to the Museum of Nature</a> as well as passes to the <a href="http://cafmuseum.techno-science.ca/en" target="_blank">Canada Agriculture and Food Museum</a>, <a href="http://www.casmuseum.techno-science.ca" target="_blank">Canada Aviation and Space Museum</a> and the <a href="http://ottawamuseumnetwork.com" target="_blank">Ottawa Museum Network</a>.</li>
</ul>

<p><br />
Don&#39;t forget to come in and check out our growing collection of books, DVDs, and magazines. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
If you just want to stay in and see what is new at the HCM Library&nbsp;and what e-resources are at your fingertips, through your computer/tablet/other device, click on the Online Resources button on our webpage to see where else you can explore, research, and read. If at anytime, you run into difficulty navigating the HCM Public Library webpage, don&#39;t hesitate to send an email to the librarian (hcmlibra13@gmail.com); she will check it out and get back to you! &nbsp;<br />
<br />
<strong>The new DVD POOL is in!</strong> &nbsp;Just click on the link below to see the movies in the pool. &nbsp;<br />
<br />
<a href="index_14_4004744971.pdf" target="_blank">DVD Pool 2016 July 29-Oct 10</a><br />
<br />
Don&#39;t forget to scan the corresponding Block ID Number card from the binder (under SOLS DVD POOL CARDS)&nbsp;in order to sign these movies out, or if you would prefer, just simply use the Sign-Out Sheets&nbsp;(in the front of the binder) using your library number and movie number&nbsp;(these DVDs do not use the&nbsp;325960000# numbering system, so&nbsp;you will need to put in&nbsp;the &quot;18 - ##&quot; that is located on the spine/front of the movie cover). &nbsp;If you have any problems, just leave a detailed note on the Librarian&#39;s desk. &nbsp;Thanks!</p>
</span>
